{"tid":1959040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲記唔記得當初我哋嘅信念","createTime":"2020-04-05T06:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:44:41.000Z","uid":254442,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3e8b81f135ce0a4e4d25cc08565e6d1ac3d9cb","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:38:51.000Z","msg":"冇大台 不篤灰 不分化 不割蓆<br />\n求大家唔好再互相批鬥啦<br />\n其實好多人都知啲五毛<br />\n根本係特登喺連登開po<br />\n就係引人去講 <br />\n基本上唔使作多餘討論 <br />\n入到去淨係拉乜鳩都唔好講<br />\n剩返講嘢嗰啲咪係五毛囉<br />\n我明大家有唔同諗法<br />\n對好多嘢都有同睇法<br />\n但係一日係呢個極權政府未倒台之前<br />\n黑警未受到制裁之前<br />\n可唔可以好似當初咁集中火力<br />\n對準政權 大家都係手足<br />\n大家嘅共同敵人都係得一個<br />\n就係共產黨<br />\n我想同大家一齊贏落去<br />\n應承我 一齊光復香港<br />\n比一個交代嗰啲過咗身嘅手足<br />\n好唔好"},{"pid":"7e738da5d586b947a6d2d4ec23160f590aa50148","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"f94c09dd230ec1bc4c800f76e01dd7e1f44d31e9","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:39:10.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"209d7f25d55c9bd6f7d9440400e6cf6bd18acb98","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"c9b9fa59c66a8dca4e859d63a4c06ff67c10621a","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"a2122d46facaeb7a88d66b752edce050f6cc526a","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"52bb94f2e7869f4fe791c01f0780f1c65d466def","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"61146ab7d910d8dd4a7b1535394c38d9731d92a1","tid":1959040,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3e8b81f135ce0a4e4d25cc08565e6d1ac3d9cb","tid":1959040,"uid":254442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"